headline: Sysco’s Q4 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: Sysco’s fourth quarter saw a marked positive market reaction as the company delivered results in line with Wall Street’s revenue expectations and slightly surpassed non-GAAP earnings forecasts. Management attributed performance to improving U.S. case volumes, disciplined expense control, and momentum in its international division. CEO Kevin Hourican noted, “Our results were enabled by improving case volume trends, strengthening gross margin performance and disciplined expense management.” Notabl
